OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine but cool start. Sunny
OL,6,Fspells through the morning, turning
OL,7,Fcloudier into the afternoon but still
OL,8,Fwith bright or sunny intervals. One or
OL,9,Ftwo showers possible, these mainly
OL,10,Ftowards Kent. Breezy but winds easing
OL,11,Flater. Temperatures near average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FGenerally dry with some clear
OL,14,Fspells at first, but cloud thickening
OL,15,Ffrom the west after midnight, bringing
OL,16,Fsome patchy rain and drizzle eastwards
OL,17,Fthrough the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
